reviews.title: Outstanding App !
reviews.comment: This is a great app, I believe the mobo team really kept their heart in this project. Its highly powerful yet free, thats really wonderful. I am really impressed with this app, I tried watching 720p resolution videos in 360p hard ware, that\'s awesome. But it still have improvements (every thing that grows does have improvements) as its not able to play HD videos(mkv, avi) on my device, it would be great if the mobo team considers this issue and optimizes this for a smooth movie watching experience(thats why 4). Apart from that  every thing is simply superb. And I am feeling great in appreciating and thanking them for their contribution to the android world. (right now I am unable to find a similar competent player)
